<li><a href='http://jamigold.com/2012/03/how-do-you-handle-disappointments/' rel='bookmark' title='How Do You Handle Disappointments?'>How Do You Handle Disappointments?</a></li>
</ol></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/jamigold?a=Osv6vEdozMk:pMvYPkRMLKc:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/jamigold?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/jamigold?a=Osv6vEdozMk:pMvYPkRMLKc:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/jamigold?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/jamigold?a=Osv6vEdozMk:pMvYPkRMLKc:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/jamigold?i=Osv6vEdozMk:pMvYPkRMLKc:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/jamigold?a=Osv6vEdozMk:pMvYPkRMLKc:JUhcmGiK9AQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/jamigold?d=JUhcmGiK9AQ" border="0"></img></a>
</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/jamigold/~4/Osv6vEdozMk" height="1" width="1"/>]]></content:encoded>
			<wfw:commentRss>http://jamigold.com/2012/05/are-you-in-this-for-the-long-haul/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
